        breeds are descendents of the wild <ENAMEX TYPE="ANIMAL">species</ENAMEX> from which they were derived. The process of
        <ENAMEX TYPE="SUBSTANCE">domestication</ENAMEX> dramatically changed the performance and genetic architecture of the
        <ENAMEX TYPE="ANIMAL">ancestral species</ENAMEX> through the process of hybridization and selection as originally
