        <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">PLoS Biology</ENAMEX> (<ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Gur</ENAMEX> and <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Zamir 2004).</ENAMEX> I will discuss how ‚Äúsmart breeding‚Äù
        <ENAMEX TYPE="ANIMAL">recycles ‚Äúold genes‚Äù</ENAMEX> to develop highly productive, <ENAMEX TYPE="DISEASE">stress</ENAMEX>-resistant modern varieties and
        why this approach is particularly attractive to increase food security in regions of the
